<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>MindNest Support</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg1: #f6fbf8;
      --bg2: #eef7f2;
      --card: rgba(255,255,255,0.82);
      --text: #203229;
      --muted: #5a6e63;
      --accent: #6da88a;
      --accent-dark: #4f866b;
      --border: rgba(109,168,138,0.20);
      --shadow: 0 18px 45px rgba(48, 86, 67, 0.12);
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      color: var(--text);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(146, 197, 168, 0.22), transparent 30%),
        radial-gradient(circle at bottom right, rgba(109, 168, 138, 0.18), transparent 28%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg1), var(--bg2));
      min-height: 100vh;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .wrap {
      width: min(960px, calc(100% - 32px));
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 32px 0 56px;
    }

    .hero {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      padding: 40px 32px;
      border-radius: 28px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.92), rgba(244,251,247,0.86));
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      margin-bottom: 22px;
    }

    .leaf {
      position: absolute;
      width: 180px;
      height: 180px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      filter: blur(2px);
      opacity: 0.18;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, #8dc0a2, #5d9375);
    }

    .leaf.one { top: -60px; right: -30px; }
    .leaf.two { bottom: -80px; left: -50px; }

    .badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 8px 14px;
      background: rgba(109, 168, 138, 0.12);
      color: var(--accent-dark);
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(34px, 5vw, 56px);
      line-height: 1.05;
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    .hero p {
      max-width: 680px;
      font-size: 18px;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin: 0;
    }

    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(12, 1fr);
      gap: 22px;
      margin-top: 22px;
    }

    .card {
      grid-column: span 12;
      background: var(--card);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 24px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      padding: 28px;
    }

    .card h2 {
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      font-size: 24px;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .card p, .card li {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .contact-box {
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
      padding: 18px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: rgba(109, 168, 138, 0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(109, 168, 138, 0.16);
      margin-top: 16px;
    }

    .faq {
      display: grid;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-top: 16px;
    }

    .faq-item {
      padding: 18px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
      border: 1px solid rgba(109, 168, 138, 0.14);
    }

    .faq-item strong {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      color: var(--text);
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    a {
      color: var(--accent-dark);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    .two-up {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-top: 16px;
    }

    .mini {
      padding: 18px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
      border: 1px solid rgba(109, 168, 138, 0.14);
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-top: 22px;
      padding: 6px;
    }

    @media (min-width: 860px) {
      .primary { grid-column: span 7; }
      .secondary { grid-column: span 5; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      .hero { padding: 28px 22px; }
      .card { padding: 22px; }
      .two-up { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .hero p { font-size: 16px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="leaf one"></div>
      <div class="leaf two"></div>
      <div class="badge">MindNest Support</div>
      <h1>We’re here to help.</h1>
      <p>
        Need help with MindNest? Whether you have a question, found a bug, or need support with your account,
        you can reach out using the contact details below.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="grid">
      <div class="card primary">
        <h2>Contact support</h2>
        <p>
          For app support, bug reports, or general questions, please contact:
        </p>

        <div class="contact-box">
          <div><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:mindnestdeveloper@gmail.com">support@yourdomain.com</a></div>
          <div><strong>Response time:</strong> We aim to reply within 2–5 business days.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq">
          <div class="faq-item">
            <strong>My entries are not syncing</strong>
            Make sure your device is connected to the internet. If you created entries while offline, MindNest can sync them automatically once your connection is restored.
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <strong>I found a bug</strong>
            Please email us with a short description of the issue, what device you are using, and any steps we can follow to reproduce it.
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <strong>Can I request a feature?</strong>
            Yes. We welcome feature suggestions and product feedback. Send us a message and we’ll review it for future updates.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card secondary">
        <h2>Helpful links</h2>
        <div class="two-up">
          <div class="mini">
            <strong>Privacy Policy</strong>
            <p>Link your hosted privacy policy page here.</p>
            <a href="https://leelyx0.github.io/MindNest-privacy/">View policy</a>
          </div>
          <div class="mini">
            <strong>App Version</strong>
            <p>Version 1.0.0</p>
            <p>Last updated: April 23, 2026</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mini" style="margin-top:16px;">
          <strong>Support tips</strong>
          <p>
            When contacting support, include your device model, iOS version, app version, and a brief explanation of the problem.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="footer">
      © 2026 MindNest. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
